'''Tabitha King''' (isem mi tlul'''Tabitha Jane Spruce''') (tlul [[24 meɣres]] [[1949]]) d [[tamyarut]] d [[tameɣnast]] [[tamarikant|tamarikant]] .

Tabitha King uqbel ad tezweǧ isemis yella d Tabitha Jane-Frances Spruce tlul di [[Old Town, Maine|Old Town]], [[Maine]]. Baba-s d Raymond George ma d yemma-s d Sarah Jane White Spruce.

Teɣra di St. Mary’s Grammar di temdint n Old Town, teffeɣ seg-s 1963. Syen tekcem ar [[John Bapst Memorial High School]] di [[Bangor, Maine|Bangor]] alamma useggas 1967, tewwid lisans ines deg umezruy deg useggas 1971 seg tesdawit [[University of Maine]] di [[Orono (town), Maine|Orono]].

==Tawacult==
Temlal Tabitha aragaz-is, amyaru ameqran [[Stephen King]], di tesnawit deg wemkan anda tella teqqar txeddem di temkarḍit Fogler . Zewǧen di 2 yennayer 1971, ɣand have three children togetherursen tlata dderya: Naomi Rachel, [[Joe Hill (amyaru)|Joseph Hillstrom]], d [[Owen King|Owen Phillip]]. Sin agi ineggura uɣalen d imyura daɣen.

==tawuri==
King tura atas n ungalen, ffɣen ar imaẓragen Macmillan d New American Library. Tura daɣen adlis nniḍen d-yeffɣen ɣur Dendrite.


==arrazen==
Deg wayyur n mayu 1987, King d wergaz-is ttunefk-asen Honorary Doctorates of Humane Letters sɣur  University of Maine di Orono.

Deg useggas 1998, fkan-as  Annual Constance Carlson Humanities Prize amezwaru i leqdic ines deg weḥric n tallalt n talsa.

